Class Entry

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.kasoki.jfeedly.model.Entry

    public class Entry
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Entry>
    Representation model of one Entry from the "/v3/entries" api call. This class is sometimes refered to as article.
